main_body:
Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 690/2008 is amended as follows:
1. in points 4, 5, 7, 8, 9 and 10 of heading (a), after the word ‘Greece’ the following words are added: ‘(until 31 March 2010)’;
2. in point 2 of heading (b), the third indent is deleted;
3. in point 01 of heading (c), the words ‘Greece (Crete and Lesvos),’ are deleted;
4. point 4 of heading (d), is replaced by the following:
‘4. Grapevine flavescence dorée MLO
